00:34:21,259 --> 00:34:23,784
Always think you're gonna hit
the big score your first night.
I'm a stupid rookie?

461
00:34:23,861 --> 00:34:27,695
How much do you want
to bet it's Kane?
A billion dollars.

462
00:34:27,765 --> 00:34:30,757
Fine.

463
00:34:30,835 --> 00:34:33,133
Get out! Get out of my store!
Look at my store!

464
00:34:33,204 --> 00:34:36,605
